{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setContentInset:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIEdgeInsets"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"contentInset"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"contentInset","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The new values to inset the content by.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Specify "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if you want the map view to animate the change to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content inset or "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if you want the map to inset the content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"code":"centerCoordinate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text